data.text:
Virtual Bird & David Rovics by davidrovics

published on 2021-04-08T23:27:07Z

It's been one of the great musical pleasures of my life to have been discovered by Virtual Bird. We're eventually going to put out an album together. I'm sharing what is, in one form or another, a work in progress, one song at a time. Or really, Virtual Bird is sharing them -- I send them the lyrics, they do literally everything else. At least that's been the process so far, with all but the first track, which I initially also wrote music for as well as lyrics.
